Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain Dedication)

The aggregated statistics, derived per-image metrics, image-to-culture
metadata, and inference prompts in this directory and the sibling
`prompts/` and `figures/` directories are dedicated to the public domain
under the CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication.

Full text: https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/legalcode

This dedication applies to the derived data produced by the analysis pipeline
described in the accompanying manuscript. Underlying source images are not
redistributed in this package; they are available under the Open Access
policies of the Metropolitan Museum of Art (CC0), the Cleveland Museum of Art
(CC0), and the National Museum of Korea (Korea's public-API regulations).
